Detailed Description

template<class OBJ, class EXC>
class GisStack< OBJ, EXC >

GisStack is an abstract template for a Stack ADT. This class is not yet part of the GisCommon API. However, doc comments have been added since it might be added to the API in the future. All doc comments will need to change to if this happens.
